---
title: Pan-fried Hake and Lentils with carrot and baby spinach
description: Heart-healthy, protein-packed, and brimming with flavour, this is one dish you don't want to miss. The spinach and lentils make the perfect bed for a golden fried flaky hake fillet.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221101_R04_W52_IE_IEXCFCLF0009-3_MB_remove_scales_edit_Main_high-032be0c3.jpg
